16:48.834 --> 16:51.000
[♪ Encouraging race music]

16:51.041 --> 16:54.250
-Oooohhh! Ah!
[♪ Encouraging race music]

16:54.291 --> 16:56.834
-[Gerry]: Oh, my leg. Again!
[♪ Music and crowd cheers]

16:56.875 --> 17:00.166
-[Gerry]: Not again, agh!
[♪ Music and crowd cheers]

17:00.208 --> 17:02.834
-[Gerry]: Ooh, agh! Foot!
[♪ Music and crowd cheers]

17:02.875 --> 17:05.041
-Agh!
-Don't wait up Gerry.

17:05.083 --> 17:07.417
I'm comin' for ya.
Glory hallelujah!

17:07.458 --> 17:09.834
-[Frank laughs]
-[Gerry grunts in pain]

17:09.875 --> 17:12.208
♪ Encouraging race music

17:12.250 --> 17:14.500
[♪ Encouraging race music]
-[Donovan Bailey]:
Too easy Gerry.

17:14.542 --> 17:17.291
-Agh! Ahhh!
[♪ Music and crowd cheers]

