17:43.125 --> 17:46.000
-You want me to sign it?

17:46.041 --> 17:48.000
-Yeah, please sign it.

17:48.041 --> 17:50.875
-Yeah, please sign it.

17:50.917 --> 17:53.458
♪ Music

17:53.500 --> 17:55.875
♪ Music

17:55.917 --> 17:57.750
-Here ya go.

17:58.667 --> 18:00.500
-Good fuck?
-Hmmm? Huh?

18:02.083 --> 18:05.834
-[Trudy]: Dear Stephan, you're a
good kid. Good fuck.
[Inhales sharply]

18:05.875 --> 18:08.291
-No, that's obviously an "l",
good luck.

18:08.333 --> 18:10.458
-[Trudy]: Not in English
it isn't.
-Bobbi?

18:10.500 --> 18:12.709
-[Bobbi]: Mmm hmm?
-What does that say?

18:12.750 --> 18:15.875
-Mmm, "you're a good kid.
Good fuck". Wow.
-No.

18:15.917 --> 18:18.959
-You see? That's why people
don't want you signing those
things.

18:19.000 --> 18:21.083
-You ruined my yearbook sir.

18:21.125 --> 18:23.291
-It's obviously a
misunderstanding.

18:23.333 --> 18:26.250
-Yeah? Tell it to the judge.
-Stephan?

18:26.291 --> 18:28.250
Luck sakes.

18:28.291 --> 18:30.709
-Ah God, they didn't even
spike the punch.

18:30.750 --> 18:33.083
What's wrong with these kids?

18:33.125 --> 18:35.291
-Hey, how ya doin'?

18:35.333 --> 18:37.709
-Just thinking about Simon.
-Yeah.

18:37.750 --> 18:41.208
-And what might have been.
Why did I have to bring pie?

18:42.417 --> 18:45.083
You know, this would have
been our song?

18:45.125 --> 18:48.875
Alright, why don't you go
check the bathrooms for pukers?

18:48.917 --> 18:51.834
-Yeah. Thanks.
-Yeah. You're welcome.

18:51.875 --> 18:54.500
♪ Music

