♪ Music

18:57.083 --> 18:59.667
-Simon! You came!

18:59.709 --> 19:01.792
-Course. I wanted to see you.

19:01.834 --> 19:05.083
-Also, I was called in to
supervise, as well.

19:05.125 --> 19:08.875
Ah, dance?
-I thought you'd never ask.

19:08.917 --> 19:11.709
-[Nisha]: That's good.
-Okay.

