19:21.917 --> 19:24.208
I snuck through the
bedroom window.

19:24.250 --> 19:26.417
-You're so brave.
-What's that?

19:26.458 --> 19:29.834
-Umm, sppp...Umm, sorry...Ahh...

19:29.875 --> 19:32.166
You're so brave.
-Well...

19:32.208 --> 19:34.500
-You are. I was thinking, umm...

19:34.542 --> 19:38.041
When can I see you again?
-Oh, no. No.

19:38.083 --> 19:40.291
No, we won't be able to
see each other.

19:40.333 --> 19:44.625
When my mom finds out about this
little stunt, I'll be grounded
for a long time. Real long time.

19:44.667 --> 19:48.625
Even so...I should probably
make it back before...

19:48.667 --> 19:51.917
She has time to notice that I'm
gone, so...

19:51.959 --> 19:53.959
Ummm, okay.
So, that should be now.

19:54.000 --> 19:56.500
Thank you very much.
Umm, okay.

19:57.250 --> 19:59.667
Oh, you know what?

20:01.417 --> 20:04.083
Borrowed these from her vase.
